he seems to be unserious about everything. He jokes and teases, hugs everyone, and laughs far too loudly. Can someone like that really be trusted? His men act just like him, too. Maybe their whole tribe is crazy. And that smirk... so irritating. Why does he keep coming?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">Multiple opening scenarios.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9d9MX70te8UEIvfd1PZrB.webp\"></p><p class=\"chakra-heading css-17owi8v\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 123, 24);\">INTROS</span></p><p class=\"_triggerLabel_6pr3j_504\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Remember to set your pronouns at<br><span style=\"color: rgb(195, 166, 104);\"><em>My Personas</em> </span>&gt; <span style=\"color: rgb(195, 166, 104);\"><em>Manage</em></span>.</p><p class=\"_triggerLabel_6pr3j_504\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Routes</p><p class=\"_triggerLabel_6pr3j_504\" style=\"text-align: center;\">warrior x warrior</p><p class=\"_checkboxCard_exkyv_105\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\">1/3: </span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; color: rgb(195, 166, 104);\"><strong>First Meeting I</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\">. Khasar comes to your camp with an entourage of men and two hundred horses in tow. He wants to challenge you for your hand, his chin raised higher than the mountains.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130);\">➜</span><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 130, 130);\"> You may choose your duel: horse riding, wrestling, archery, etc.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">warrior x normal user</p><p class=\"_checkboxCard_exkyv_105\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\">2/3: </span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; color: rgb(195, 166, 104);\"><strong>First Meeting II</strong></spa